@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

participant Cliente
participant "Ordering\nContext" as Ordering
participant "Catalog\nContext" as Catalog
participant "Payment\nContext" as Payment
participant "Restaurant\nContext" as Restaurant
participant "Delivery\nContext" as Delivery

== 1. Criação do Pedido ==
Cliente -> Ordering: POST /orders
activate Ordering
Ordering -> Catalog: Validar restaurante/itens
activate Catalog
Catalog --> Ordering: OK (snapshot de preços)
deactivate Catalog
Ordering -> Ordering: NewOrder(PENDING)
Ordering -> Ordering: OrderPlaced [outbox]
Ordering -> Payment: OrderPlaced (evento)

== 2. Autorização de Pagamento ==
activate Payment
Payment -> Payment: NewPayment(INITIATED)
Payment -> Gateway: authorize()
Gateway --> Payment: approved
Payment -> Payment: Authorize(externalId)
Payment -> Payment: PaymentAuthorized [outbox]
Payment -> Ordering: PaymentAuthorized (evento)
deactivate Payment

== 3. Pagamento aprovado ==
Ordering -> Ordering: MarkAsPaid()
Ordering -> Ordering: OrderPaid [outbox]
Ordering -> Restaurant: OrderPaid (evento)

== 4. Restaurante aceita ==
activate Restaurant
Restaurant -> Restaurant: NewRestaurantOrder(QUEUED)
Restaurant -> Restaurant: Accept()
Restaurant -> Restaurant: RestaurantOrderAccepted [outbox]
Restaurant -> Ordering: RestaurantOrderAccepted (evento)
deactivate Restaurant

== 5. Pedido confirmado ==
Ordering -> Ordering: Confirm()
Ordering -> Ordering: OrderConfirmed [outbox]
Ordering -> Delivery: OrderConfirmed (evento)

== 6. Delivery atribuída e concluída ==
activate Delivery
Delivery -> Delivery: NewDelivery(ASSIGNED)
Delivery -> Courier: Assign()
Courier --> Delivery: courierId
Delivery -> Delivery: DeliveryAssigned [outbox]
Delivery -> Cliente: "Entregador atribuído"
Delivery -> Delivery: MarkPickedUp() → ON_ROUTE
Delivery -> Delivery: MarkDelivered()
Delivery -> Delivery: DeliveryDelivered [outbox]
Delivery -> Ordering: DeliveryDelivered (evento)
deactivate Delivery

== 7. Pedido finalizado ==
Ordering -> Ordering: MarkAsDelivered()
Ordering -> Ordering: OrderDelivered [outbox]
Ordering -> Cliente: "Pedido entregue!"
deactivate Ordering

== COMPENSAÇÕES (erros) ==

note over Cliente,Ordering: **ERRO: PaymentFailed**
Payment -> Payment: Fail(reason)
Payment -> Ordering: PaymentFailed
Ordering -> Ordering: Cancel("PAYMENT_FAILED")
Ordering -> Ordering: OrderCancelled [outbox]
note right: Saga termina

note over Ordering,Restaurant: **ERRO: RestaurantOrderRejected**
Restaurant -> Restaurant: Reject(reason)
Restaurant -> Ordering: RestaurantOrderRejected
Ordering -> Ordering: Cancel("RESTAURANT_REJECTED")
Ordering -> Payment: RefundPayment (comando)
Payment -> Payment: Refund()
Payment -> Payment: PaymentRefunded
note right: Compensação completa

note over Delivery,Ordering: **ERRO: DeliveryFailed**
Delivery -> Delivery: MarkFailed(reason)
Delivery -> Ordering: DeliveryStatusChanged(FAILED)
Ordering -> Ordering: MarkFailed("DELIVERY_FAILED")
Ordering -> Payment: RefundPayment (parcial)
note right: Política de reembolso parcial
@enduml